  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "What is HyperFrames? Video, with HTML. Just an HTML file plus GSAP.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c856f819cfe1d1ae8d112406ae464f21fd52373be30ba807d8dd7af4b63d9350",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 5.38702947845805,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "To start, npx hyperframes init. No build step.",
      "checksum": "sha256:86d86e21b34d21e2345069c0be14bf1ab851f7978f445da27e4a083f6eb82b35",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 12
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "No config. Three rules to remember. Number one. data-start tells the renderer when each clip enters and exits.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6e4dabe9195fc9781c55cb14dc204488bc985384d2b47c81e9e3925d9fbbcdb8",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 7.569705215419501,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 20
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Number two. class equals clip controls visibility.",
      "checksum": "sha256:072c527dbe22ee226678835d489fe1fc269d92bc1f4379a8c7b31bfe1b7d942d",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 3.3436734693877552,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 38
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Number three. Register your GSAP timeline on window dot double-underscore timelines.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ae89fe2cdea3055864ec66e42279420faff2c083962718f00874068d03d5fe2a",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 5.201269841269841,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 45
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Then npx hyperframes preview to view in the browser. npx hyperframes render to ship an MP4.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5e20eb7d3ff950e6a5e5c5ef4937cf22ae84517cdc45bac5f3dcc40c101cb19b",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 5.851428571428571,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 56
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Deterministic. No randomness. No clocks.",
      "checksum": "sha256:783993c8695a7e242774f7c76ab434b19eabbaa34386bdb6a0c39e256e63e3d6",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 2.3219954648526078,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 72
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "No network at render time. Docs are at hyperframes dot heygen dot com.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cd46ea16f0bce215f218dcd38fb6a87be6d5e2e10496e2f0b90227878a69ee5c",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 4.2260317460317465,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 77
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Subscribe for more breakdowns.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3a1e6eb76446ddf505a1c06d8cfe7864834e55c7de57182631d8faa8e38b9d50",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 1.7182766439909296,
